Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:21.98,花語製作通用-ja,,0,0,0,,本字幕由✿花語&千夏字幕組✿共同製作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.62,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,タバコぐらいいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.92,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I can at least have a little cigarette, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.78,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,吸うのが得意そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.66,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You look good at sucking on stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.04,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.16,Default,av,0,0,0,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の替わりにオルコをやってくれるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:34.65,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I heard you'll kill Orco for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:37.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.30,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あ お安い御用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.42,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That'll save me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,手間がはぶげるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で どうやんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.43,Default,fan,0,0,0,,So, how's it happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.34,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつがお前に策があると言ってんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:47.26,Default,fan,0,0,0,,This guy told me you had a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.79,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Like hell I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.80,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえよ そんなもん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.84,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,腹がへいすぎて頭が働かねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.62,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry, I can't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,飯くれ 後酒もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.70,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Get me some food and booze as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:01.16,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここんとこまともなもん食ってねんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I haven't had a proper meal in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:08.28,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうも立場が分かってねえぇようだな ボイー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:07.07,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You don't seem to grasp the position you're in, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.78,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,舐めろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:13.37,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Lick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:17.72,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前菜替わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.91,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Think of it as an appetizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.95,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,イタリア産のいい肉使ってるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:20.94,Default,fan,0,0,0,,They're made from fine Italian cows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:40.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした イタリアの足を早く食わせろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:40.11,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Don't I get to eat my Italian shanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:47.96,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか食わせてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.58,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey! Get this guy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.37,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロに逃げられたらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.34,Default,or,0,0,0,,I hear Nero got away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:04.83,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あ 探し出してやるつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:04.81,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Yes, we still intend to find and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:09.76,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで通り あなたとは仲良くやっていきたいと思ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:09.65,Default,ron,0,0,0,,We hope to continue our good relationship with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.84,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためには奴が邪魔でしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.84,Default,ron,0,0,0,,He's standing in the way of that however.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.31,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Mr. Orco, have you heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.62,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコさん 何かお耳に入ってませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:21.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最近 羽振りがいいらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.24,Default,or,0,0,0,,I hear he's doing quite well for himself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何のことです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:23.68,Default,ron,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:28.98,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ローレス べブンとかいう酒で しこたま儲けてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.61,Default,or,0,0,0,,He's rolling in dough from a drink called Lawless Heaven, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.90,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは ネロが勝手に作らせてる酒で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.87,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Yeah, Nero started making that without asking us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.24,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も一枚噛ませろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.24,Default,or,0,0,0,,I want a slice of that pie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.46,Default,ron,0,0,0,,of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.49,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロさえ捕まえれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.70,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If we get our hands on Nero,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:43.86,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その酒のレシピや蒸留所も手に入ります
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:43.42,Default,ron,0,0,0,,we'll have both the recipe and the brewery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:47.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か分かりましたら 連絡をください
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.82,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If you find anything out, get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:51.18,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これはガラッシアの希望でもあります
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.70,Default,ron,0,0,0,,That's a request from the Galassias, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.21,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,では 失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.75,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Well, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ひよっこが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.03,Default,or,0,0,0,,Little whelp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.84,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラッシア風吹かせやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.76,Default,or,0,0,0,,Throwing Galassia's weight around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.86,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これでネロも終わりか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.82,Default,or,0,0,0,,I guess Nero's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:17.10,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さて うちの跳ねっ返りもどうにでしまわねぇとな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:16.82,Default,or,0,0,0,,Now, we've got to do something about our little spitfire as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.56,Default,or,0,0,0,,For heaven's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:25.24,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こう悩みが多くじゃ 飯も喉取らねえや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:24.97,Default,or,0,0,0,,I've got so much on my mind, I can barely eat a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.21,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい ラザニアはまだか?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.77,Default,or,0,0,0,,Hey! Where's that lasagna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.03,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}kanjou ni tsukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.03,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}I can assign whatever name I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.03,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}namae wa jiyuu dane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.03,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}To these emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:49.03,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}hora kawarihateta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:49.03,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}See, they've already ceased to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.12,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}kesenai boku no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.12,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}The trigger of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.42,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}tsumi no hikigane ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.42,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}My unrepentable sins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.79,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}toketeshimaisou de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.79,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}Seems ready to melt away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.59,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}nikushimi ga kieteshimattara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.59,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}But if this hatefulness fades,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.22,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}kimi o korosenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.22,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}I'll lose my chance to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.69,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}kako o tannou shiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.69,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}I'm experiencing every moment of my past,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:24.23,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}tsumi ga tsukutta boku ni kawaru tame ni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:24.23,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}Trying to become the person who created these sins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.24,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}ASL no naifu de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.24,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}With an ASL knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:35.62,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}kioku no signal kizamareteru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:35.62,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}Despite the signal carved into my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:47.34,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}itami sae keshisatteshimau kizuna no spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:47.34,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}Even the pain is erased away by this spiral of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:58.85,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}Having wandered in, I begin to fade... ceasing to be myself.
