Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ 寝心地は悪くなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.35,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I slept okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:17.46,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,文句を言える立場じゃないが それにしても...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:17.39,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We're in no position to complain, but even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.88,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Tigre's gonna pull through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.18,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,テガレが助かったってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.33,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.44,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしまぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:26.09,Default,nero,0,0,0,,But if we can't kill Orco, we'll all be fish food soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:26.11,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコをやれなきゃ 皆纏めて魚の餌だがな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:30.10,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ 本当何も考え ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.24,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Avilio, do you really not have—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.10,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:29.89,Default,av,0,0,0,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.04,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とっておきのがな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,I've got a perfect one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも お前 あの時...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.34,Default,vol,0,0,0,,But you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.34,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコに漏れたら終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.08,Default,av,0,0,0,,If it gets back to Orco, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:39.56,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってる人間は少なければ少ないほどいい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:39.44,Default,av,0,0,0,,The fewer people who know about it, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.78,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で どうやる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.53,Default,bar,0,0,0,,So, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.76,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ボルペ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.36,Default,av,0,0,0,,Volpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,鶏を一匹捕まえてきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,I want you to catch me a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.57,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ いただこうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.53,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Come on, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,随分と警備の行き届いた店じゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Pretty tight security for a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.59,Default,man,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:13.28,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 ネロだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.50,Default,man,0,0,0,,You're Nero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.42,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何の用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.49,Default,man,0,0,0,,What do you want here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.38,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ飯食いに行きやったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.35,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I came all the way out here for a good meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.30,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それとビジネスね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:22.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Also I've got business to discuss, so let Don Orco know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.34,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン オルコと繋いでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.51,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ボディチェックだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.50,Default,man,0,0,0,,You'll need a pat-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここのお勧めは何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.60,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What do you recommend here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.16,Default,man,0,0,0,,The lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Just like mom used to make, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.96,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ママの味か?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,入れ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.21,Default,man,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.70,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぉ ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.55,Default,or,0,0,0,,Hey, Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:50.70,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,良くも まぁ 俺様の前に面出せたな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:50.94,Default,or,0,0,0,,Didn't think you'd have the guts to show your face around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.03,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここがどこか 分かってんのかい?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.03,Default,or,0,0,0,,Don't you know where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.60,Default,nero,0,0,0,,"Ottimo Orco."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.88,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オッティモ オルコ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:58.92,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ローレスで一番旨いレストラン だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.47,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The best restaurant in Lawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.89,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.90,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.88,Default,or,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.98,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,弟達が探してたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.12,Default,or,0,0,0,,Your brother's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.76,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今の塒は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.44,Default,or,0,0,0,,Where are you holed up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.50,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,失敗した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.07,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.98,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.79,Default,or,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.22,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで食ったなかで最高のラザニアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:24.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,This is the best lasagna I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.15,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I should've joined the Orco family instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.15,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オルコファミリーに入っとけきゃ良かったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:35.18,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,面白いこと言う奴だ なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.68,Default,or,0,0,0,,Hey, he's a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.05,Default,or,0,0,0,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.66,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にはお前を殺す理由が山程ある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:47.44,Default,or,0,0,0,,I have many reasons to kill you and not a single one to let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,活かしとく理由はこれぽっちもねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.44,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, I came out here to see you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.38,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ワザワザ来たんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,話くらい聞いても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.66,Default,nero,0,0,0,,At least hear me out—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.46,Default,or,0,0,0,,What could you possibly have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.56,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今更 何の話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.67,Default,or,0,0,0,,It'd better not be a plea for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.84,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,命乞いは聞かねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:01.45,Default,or,0,0,0,,I've known your father, Vincent, for 40 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.02,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の親父 ヴィンセントとは40年来の顔馴染みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.56,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達はいい関係でやってた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.51,Default,or,0,0,0,,We had a good relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それをお前がぶち壊した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.43,Default,or,0,0,0,,You ruined that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:12.16,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達の酒を散々くすねやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.97,Default,or,0,0,0,,by stealing all of our booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You've done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:16.12,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃお互い様だ そういう商売だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.10,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That's the nature of the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.17,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の晩餐は終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.13,Default,or,0,0,0,,The Last Supper is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.92,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最高の酒を飲んで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.35,Default,or,0,0,0,,Have some of the finest whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.05,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心置き無く あの世へ逝け
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:32.02,Default,or,0,0,0,,I want to send you to your grave with no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:40.39,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかい じゃ 遠慮なく頂くぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:40.37,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Is it? Happy to try it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:47.11,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブーツレッグか ウィンザーの年代物だな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Bootleg, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Finely aged, from Windsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.96,Default,or,0,0,0,,Good nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.88,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いい鼻だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.98,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,30年物は滅多に飲めねぇだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.22,Default,or,0,0,0,,Not every day you get to drink one that's aged 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.99,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お口に召したか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.96,Default,or,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.12,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ お上品な味だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.25,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's got a refined flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.91,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 今の味じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.89,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That said, it's not the flavor of the modern day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:27.31,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,飲んでみな ほやほやの一ヶ月物だけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's brand new, from just a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.49,Default,av,0,0,0,,No, three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 三週間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.91,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.95,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:54.34,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うめぇな これがローレス ヘブンか?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.36,Default,or,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.44,Default,or,0,0,0,,This is Lawless Heaven, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この酒がありゃ ワザワザさつに金握らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:58.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,With this, you wouldn't have to pay off cops
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.60,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,国境から運んでくる必要もなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,to smuggle stuff across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.14,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見返りは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.11,Default,or,0,0,0,,What do you want in exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.55,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Don! You can't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン こんな奴の言うことなんて...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.84,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.28,Default,or,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:12.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Make us a place to lie low and I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:12.66,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達の塒を用意してくれるなら そっくりくれてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.03,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何をだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.01,Default,or,0,0,0,,What'll you give me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.50,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全てさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.28,Default,nero,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.16,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,炭鉱跡じゃねぇか?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.11,Default,or,0,0,0,,An old coal mine, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:27.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,石炭でも掘るのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.51,Default,or,0,0,0,,Are we going to dig up some coal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.36,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お目当ては真っ暗な穴の中だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.48,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Our destination is deep in that black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.59,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつと見て来い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.55,Default,or,0,0,0,,Go with him and have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ライター持ってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You got a lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.74,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.58,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.85,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アヴィリオとか言ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.68,Default,or,0,0,0,,Avilio, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.74,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴをやろうとして奴だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.69,Default,or,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one who tried to kill Fango?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:53.07,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴの奴はパンツ一丁で逃げ出したそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.05,Default,or,0,0,0,,I hear Fango went running off in his underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.46,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ 野良猫みたいに逃げてった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.62,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah, he scrambled off like a stray cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:11:00.57,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あん時 やっといてもらえば 良かったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.54,Default,or,0,0,0,,I wish you'd killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.29,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,手紙を寄越したのはあんたか?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.26,Default,av,0,0,0,,Are you the one who sent me the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.66,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,手紙?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:07.25,Default,or,0,0,0,,Letter? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.29,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何の話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.27,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.44,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を使わないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.39,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why not use me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.74,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロはもう終わりだ だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.48,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nero's finished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.24,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,信用できねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.27,Default,or,0,0,0,,I can't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:23.06,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の本当の名前はアンジェロ ラグーザだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,My real name is Angelo Lagusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:26.02,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親父の名前はテスタ ラグーザ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,My father's name was Testa Lagusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.57,Default,or,0,0,0,,Lagusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.60,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ラグーザ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.28,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確か だいぶ前に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.05,Default,or,0,0,0,,That's right... Years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:37.08,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親父を殺したのはヴィンセント ヴァネッティだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.96,Default,av,0,0,0,,It was Vincent Vanetti who killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.08,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:39.94,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:49.71,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところで作ってやがってのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.68,Default,or,0,0,0,,So this is where you've been making it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:53.32,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このロッジと あの酒のレシピがあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:55.33,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Between the Lodge here and our recipe, this town would be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.22,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この町はあんたのもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,レシピは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.51,Default,or,0,0,0,,What's the recipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.22,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それを教えたら俺は用済みだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.21,Default,nero,0,0,0,,If I told you that, you wouldn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.17,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.50,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.85,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう解いてくれでもいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You can take them off now, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.74,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一杯やろうじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.76,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Let's have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.22,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,固めの杯ってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We can toast our new partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.44,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.58,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.15,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,びびてんじゃねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.13,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Quit jumping at shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちはオレンジビターを加えたやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.53,Default,nero,0,0,0,,This one has some orange bitters added.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.12,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一杯どうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.21,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Have a glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.70,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さぁ やってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.79,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Go on, drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,旨いぜぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぃ のまねぇかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you gonna drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.82,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Come on, that's valuable merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.00,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぃおぃ 大事な商品だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ 好きにすりゃいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.26,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空だっただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It was empty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:43.18,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロ てめぇ 嵌めやがったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.62,Default,or,0,0,0,,Damn you, Nero! You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.11,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,動きつれい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.10,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hard to move with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.62,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.33,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.38,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネロ ヴァネッティ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.11,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nero Vanetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.05,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この時を待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.70,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,銃を捨てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.65,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Give up your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン 此奴もやっちまえましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:36.84,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Don, we should kill him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.04,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうも 得体が知れねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.06,Default,cor,0,0,0,,He's completely untrustworthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,土壇場で仲間を売るなんざ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.55,Default,cor,0,0,0,,He sold him out at the last—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:46.30,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は此奴の何を知ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:45.84,Default,or,0,0,0,,What would you know about him, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,此奴はなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.02,Default,or,0,0,0,,This kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちり親の仇を討った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.59,Default,or,0,0,0,,He avenged his dead father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.64,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見上げた男だぜぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.16,Default,or,0,0,0,,He's to be admired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.24,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぃ 縄を解いてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:57.10,Default,or,0,0,0,,Hey! Untie him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:00.47,Default,man,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! There was an exit at the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.66,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,す すみません 裏に出口があって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.04,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げられました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.95,Default,man,0,0,0,,He got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:03.24,Default,or,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.12,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.94,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,捕まえるまで帰ってくんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:06.92,Default,or,0,0,0,,Don't come back until you've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.32,Default,man,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.46,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.22,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,使えねぇ奴ばっかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.93,Default,or,0,0,0,,They're all useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.88,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一杯やろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.78,Default,av,0,0,0,,Let's have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.80,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぉ そいつはいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.34,Default,or,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.42,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,バネッティも ついでにファンゴも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:31.47,Default,or,0,0,0,,Vanetti and Fango while we're at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.28,Default,or,0,0,0,,They're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.32,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.36,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファミリーに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.21,Default,or,0,0,0,,To family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.54,Default,av,0,0,0,,To family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.66,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファミリーに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.44,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,此奴は本当にうめぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:45.44,Default,or,0,0,0,,This really is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:49.42,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おぃ ネロをやっちまったが レシピは残ってんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:49.66,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Hey, we killed Nero. Can we still get the recipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.33,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あ これを作ったのは俺の知り合いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:53.13,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's made by a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにこの酒さえあればもう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.64,Default,or,0,0,0,,With this booze in our hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:00.12,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラッシアに頭を下げなくて済みそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:00.14,Default,or,0,0,0,,we'll never have to kowtow to the Galassias again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.55,Default,or,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.66,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ど どうしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,急に酔いが...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.11,Default,or,0,0,0,,I suddenly... feel so drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:23.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.42,Default,or,0,0,0,,What's... going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Here. The goods you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ お望みの品物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.86,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,Good morning ドン オルコ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.74,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Good morning, Don Orco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.94,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お目覚めですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.94,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Welcome back to the waking world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.54,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.83,Default,or,0,0,0,,Fango! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:09.00,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,てめぇ いい加減な作り話を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.01,Default,or,0,0,0,,You made up that whole story...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ざまねえな ドン オルコ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:14.14,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You're in a sad way, Don Orco.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.08,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何が望みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.05,Default,or,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:22.91,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が持ってるもの すべてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:22.88,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I want... everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.60,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時 家に入ってきたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.69,Default,av,0,0,0,,Three men came into the house that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:36.36,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴィンセント ネロ バァンノの三人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:36.24,Default,av,0,0,0,,Vincent, Nero, and Vanno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.56,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも ネロは４人って言ってたんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.55,Default,cor,0,0,0,,But Nero said there were four...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.56,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,4人目って一体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.36,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Who could the fourth be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.12,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,手紙の差出人はオルコだと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:46.00,Default,av,0,0,0,,I thought it was Orco who sent the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.65,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァネッティと敵対してるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.64,Default,av,0,0,0,,He's no friend of Vanetti's,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.36,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけと違った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.55,Default,av,0,0,0,,but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:54.08,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 この親父の親友ってやつが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,I think this "friend of my father's"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.57,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,第4の男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:55.55,Default,av,0,0,0,,was the fourth man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:18:01.95,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは後悔の気持ちから復讐を手伝おうとしてるってこと?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:18:01.95,Default,cor,0,0,0,,And he wants to help you with your revenge, out of a sense of remorse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:02.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.84,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.48,Default,av,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.67,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よ あの世話になった鶏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.66,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, that chicken that helped us out back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.44,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんがり荼毘に付してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We got it cooked up nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.24,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか真に迫ってたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.99,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I almost believed it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:25.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「ネロ ヴァネッティ この時を待っていたってなあ」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:24.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,"Nero Vanetti! I've been waiting for this moment!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.50,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.73,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかりと気持ちを込めたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.72,Default,av,0,0,0,,I really put my heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.28,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の撃たれっぷり 悪くなかったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:33.27,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I played dead pretty good, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:36.72,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're a real ham actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.88,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大した大根役者だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.53,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.50,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Shaddup...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.40,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.42,Default,av,0,0,0,,I guess it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.88,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ジェットマン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.51,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:50.10,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'm so honored to have all the executives
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:51.70,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本日長年ファミリーを支えてこられた幹部の皆様に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:55.53,Default,fan,0,0,0,,who've supported the family over the years here in one room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:55.98,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お集まり頂き 誠に光栄です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:05.74,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さて オルコファミリーは今日からファンゴファミリーになるわけだが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.98,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.60,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Starting today, the Orco family \Nbecomes the Fango family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.76,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,異存のあるやつがいねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.57,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Anyone got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:15.62,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当然この店もオッティモ ファンゴに生ませ変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:15.37,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Of course, this place is gonna \Nbecome "Ottimo Fango," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:20.48,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺として はトン オルコの作りあげてきたここの味は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:23.34,Default,fan,0,0,0,,However, I wanna keep the dishes Don Orco cultivated here just the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:23.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何っとしても守っていきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.28,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.29,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:32.50,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トン オルが拘り続けてきた料理は何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:32.45,Default,fan,0,0,0,,What's the dish Don Orco was most obsessed with perfecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:36.17,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ラザニアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.14,Default,cor,0,0,0,,L-Lasagna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:39.98,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yes! Lasagna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.97,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし ラザニア
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:44.42,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ラザニアこそオッティモ オルコの誇るメニューだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:44.41,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Lasagna was Ottimo Orco's most famous dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:49.70,Default,fan,0,0,0,,And of course, Ottimo Fango's gonna keep it going strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:50.26,720通用注釋-ja,,0,0,0,,聽不懂 純腦補 求高人指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:50.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そして勿論オッティモ ファンゴもその味は???
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.74,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした コルボ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.32,Default,fan,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Corvo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:22.95,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You think my lasagna's poisoned or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:22.97,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のラザニアに毒が入っているとでも?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.67,Default,cor,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.94,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,い いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:35.98,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ ゆっくりとその舌で味わってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:35.96,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Go on. Really {\i1}savor{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.65,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,旨い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:58.26,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ じゃんじゃん食ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.77,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yeah! Go on, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.76,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,旨い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.69,Default,man,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.20,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.91,Default,cor,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.56,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドン オルコにも食べてもらいたかったなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.37,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I wish Don Orco could have some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.58,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それ無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.52,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.28,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.28,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何故
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:18.71,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Because... you're eating what was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:18.88,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはお前 てめえらが平らげちまったからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.68,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これで終わりか?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.73,Default,man,0,0,0,,Is this all there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:23.90,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,残念 何杯でも食えそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.58,Default,man,0,0,0,,Shame, I could have eaten a lot more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:29.14,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや お代わりはたっぷりあるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.05,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:29.10,Default,fan,0,0,0,,There's {\i1}plenty{\i0} more to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:22:02.14,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ 旨いか 旨いか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.82,Default,fan,0,0,0,,How is it? Delicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.04,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Delicious, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:09.22,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もうこんな油っぽいのも食えるのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:09.28,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You can eat this greasy stuff already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:10.08,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.28,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり無理するんな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.36,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Don't force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.90,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:14.02,Default,tig,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.82,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 一先ず乗り切ったなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.72,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we made it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:20.48,Default,bar,0,0,0,,No, it's actually just going to get harder from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:20.52,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや むしろこれからが大変だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.34,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,飯がまずくなるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:23.36,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, you're ruining the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:25.34,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 鶏食え 鶏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.39,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Go on, eat your chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:28.72,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ファンゴの敵はまだいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.68,Default,av,0,0,0,,Fango still has enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.78,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そして そいつらは俺達の敵でもある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.83,Default,av,0,0,0,,Now, they've become our enemies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:35.42,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何が言いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.33,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:45.06,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,食べよう 折角のラザニアが冷める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.36,Default,av,0,0,0,,We should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.76,Default,av,0,0,0,,The lasagna will get cold.
